</p><table-wrap id="TB0516-1"><label>Table 1</label><caption><title>Measurements of the air space between inferior turbinate and septum and its relation to medial non-bony (mucosa) layer of the inferior turbinate</title></caption><table rules="all"><colgroup align="left" span="7"><col align="left" width="29.52%"/><col align="left" width="9.82%"/><col align="left" width="11.7%"/><col align="left" width="12.66%"/><col align="left" width="11.84%"/><col align="left" width="11.7%"/><col align="left" width="12.76%"/></colgroup><thead><tr><th valign="bottom" align="left" rowspan="2">Measurements</th><th valign="bottom" align="left" colspan="2">Right</th><th valign="bottom" align="left" rowspan="2">
